title: Dispenser for flags

claims.preamble: The ornamental design for a dispenser for flags, as shown and described.

description: FIG. 1 is an isometric view of a dispenser for flags according to the present invention;
FIG. 2 is a front view of the dispenser for flags illustrated in FIG. 1, the rear view being a mirror image thereof;
FIG. 3 is a right side view of the dispenser for flags illustrated in FIG. 1, the left side view being a mirror image thereof;
FIG. 4 is a top plan view of the dispenser for flags illustrated in FIG. 1; and,
FIG. 5 is a bottom plan view of the dispenser for flags illustrated in FIG. 1.
The structure depicted by means of broken lines in the figures has been shown for illustrative purposes only and forms no part of the claimed design.
